examples.en: With winter approaching, many animals are storing food.
Smokers may be storing up disease for their unborn children.
The warehouse will hold more than 90,000 pallets storing 30 million Easter eggs.
You can ripen the fruit by placing it in a paper bag and storing it at room temperature for a few days.
Squirrels are storing up nuts for the winter.
He keeps a hoard of empty yogurt containers in his basement workshop for storing whatnots.
